OL,5, A family was "left in tears" after a   
OL,6, thoughtful Royal Mail driver left a    
OL,7, gift for a disabled man who regularly  
OL,8, waves at traffic.                      
OL,10,FAlex Chesters, 27, who has quadriplegic
OL,11,Fcerebral palsy, watches from a bridge  
OL,12,Fover the M6 near Stafford, his family  
OL,13,Fsaid.                                  
OL,15,FThe toy truck was left with a          
OL,16,Fhandwritten note from a driver who     
OL,17,Fnoticed him waving.                    
OL,19,FHis family said they would like to meet
OL,20,Fthe driver and "shake his hand".       
